import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react';
import { 
  Dialog, DialogTitle, DialogContent, DialogActions, 
  TextField, Button, FormControlLabel, Checkbox, Grid 
} from '@mui/material';

const ProductFormDialog = ({ open, mode, initialData, onClose, onSubmit }) => {
  const [product, setProduct] = useState({
    id: '', // Ensures ID is included
    amazon_url: '',
    asin: '',
    price: '',
    moq: '',
    qty: '',
    upc: '',
    cost: '',
    vendor: '',
    lead_time: '',
    exp_date: '',
    fob: '',
    vendor_id: '',
    profit_moq: '',
    image_url: '',
    title: '',
    category: '',
    out_of_stock: false,
    walmart_url: '',
    ebay_url: '',
    estimated_sales_per_month: '',
    estimated_profit_per_unit: ''
  });

  useEffect(() => {
    if (initialData) {
      setProduct(prev => ({
        ...prev,
        ...initialData, 
        id: String(initialData.id ?? initialData._id ?? '') // Ensure ID is handled properly
      }));
    }
  }, [initialData]);

  const handleChange = (e) => {
    const { name, value } = e.target;
    setProduct(prev => ({ ...prev, [name]: value }));
  };

  const handleCheckboxChange = (e) => {
    const { name, checked } = e.target;
    setProduct(prev => ({ ...prev, [name]: checked }));
  };

  const handleSubmit = () => {
    onSubmit(product);
  };

  return (
    <Dialog open={open} onClose={onClose} maxWidth="md" fullWidth>
      <DialogTitle>{mode === 'edit' ? 'Edit Product' : 'Add Product'}</DialogTitle>
      <DialogContent>
        <Grid container spacing={2}>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField label="Amazon URL" name="amazon_url" value={product.amazon_url} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField label="ASIN" name="asin" value={product.asin} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
            <TextField label="Price" name="price" type="number" value={product.price} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
            <TextField label="MOQ" name="moq" type="number" value={product.moq} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
            <TextField label="Quantity" name="qty" type="number" value={product.qty} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField label="UPC" name="upc" value={product.upc} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField label="Cost" name="cost" type="number" value={product.cost} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField label="Vendor" name="vendor" value={product.vendor} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField label="Lead Time" name="lead_time" value={product.lead_time} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField label="Exp Date" name="exp_date" value={product.exp_date} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField label="FOB" name="fob" value={product.fob} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField label="Vendor ID" name="vendor_id" value={product.vendor_id} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField label="Profit MOQ" name="profit_moq" type="number" value={product.profit_moq} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <TextField label="Image URL" name="image_url" value={product.image_url} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <TextField label="Title" name="title" value={product.title} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField label="Category" name="category" value={product.category} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <FormControlLabel
              control={<Checkbox checked={product.out_of_stock} onChange={handleCheckboxChange} name="out_of_stock" />}
              label="Out of Stock"
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField label="Walmart URL" name="walmart_url" value={product.walmart_url} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField label="eBay URL" name="ebay_url" value={product.ebay_url} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField label="Estimated Sales per Month" name="estimated_sales_per_month" type="number" value={product.estimated_sales_per_month} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
            <TextField label="Estimated Profit per Unit" name="estimated_profit_per_unit" type="number" value={product.estimated_profit_per_unit} onChange={handleChange} fullWidth />
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </DialogContent>
      <DialogActions>
        <Button onClick={onClose} color="secondary">Cancel</Button>
        <Button onClick={handleSubmit} color="primary">{mode === 'edit' ? 'Update' : 'Add'}</Button>
      </DialogActions>
    </Dialog>
  );
};

export default ProductFormDialog;
